十二水合'''硫酸铝铵'''，俗名'''铵明矾'''，化学式NH<sub>4</sub>Al(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·12H<sub>2</sub>O。在一些應用中會用到少量的硫酸铝铵，天然的十二水合硫酸铝铵是一種名為{{link-en|tschermigite|tschermigite}}的礦物<ref name="RubberBible">{{RubberBible62nd|pages=B-74, B-75}}.</ref>。

== 性质 ==
硫酸铝铵为无色、透明[[结晶|结晶體]]或白色粉末。其微溶于[[水|水]]、稀酸和[[甘油|甘油]]，水溶性呈[[酸性|酸性]]。不溶于[[醇|醇]]。

== 制法 ==
由[[硫酸铝|硫酸铝]]溶液与[[硫酸铵|硫酸铵]]溶液反应，并经冷却结晶、离心分离、洗涤和干燥制得。
:<math>\rm \ Al_2(SO_4)_3+(NH_4)_2SO_4+12H_2O\rightarrow 2NH_4Al(SO_4)_2\cdot 12H_2O</math>

==用途==
硫酸铝铵不是主要的工業化學品或是實驗室常用的化學藥品，但因為它無毒且價格便宜，因此常用在一些利基型的應用中，例如水的淨化、植物膠、瓷器水泥、[[體香劑|體香劑]]、[[皮革|皮革]]製造、染整及防火織料<ref>{{citation | url = http://www.questia.com/library/encyclopedia/alum.jsp | contribution = Alum | title = The Columbia Encyclopedia | year = 2004 | edition = 6th | publisher = Columbia University Press | location = Ithaca, NY | accessdate = 2009-11-23 | archive-date = 2009-10-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091017095045/http://www.questia.com/library/encyclopedia/alum.jsp | dead-url = no }}.</ref>。硫酸铝铵可以抑制細菌生長<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefword.org.uk/reviews/2004/03/natural_deodora |language=en |title=Natural deodorants |author=Kery Saegert |publisher=the f word |date=2004-03-16 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726090905/http://www.thefword.org.uk/reviews/2004/03/natural_deodora |dead-url=no }}</ref>，硫酸铝铵和[[汗水|汗水]]混合的水溶液，其[[pH|pH]]值一般會在微酸的範圍內，約為4至5<ref>{{citation | url = http://hazard.com/msds/mf/baker/baker/files/a2760.htm | title = Aluminum Ammonium Sulfate Material Safety Data Sheet | publisher = J. T. Baker | date = March 2009 | accessdate = 2009-11-23 | archive-date = 2011-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110928025935/http://hazard.com/msds/mf/baker/baker/files/a2760.htm | dead-url = no }}.</ref>。

硫酸铝铵是動物驅蟲噴霧劑的常見成份<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.bruceharris.com.au/BHPMweb/dter_faq.htm |title=D-TER Animal and Bird Repellent |publisher=Bruce Harris Project Management Pty Ltd |date=2004-09-04 |accessdate=2010-03-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091015031644/http://bruceharris.com.au/BHPMweb/dter_faq.htm |archivedate=2009-10-15 }}.</ref><ref>{{citation | url = http://www.multicrop.com.au/MSDS/Scat_MSDS.doc | title = Scat Material Safety Data Sheet | publisher = Multicrop (Aust.) Pty. Ltd. | date = 2003-03-04 | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | archive-date = 2011-07-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110706110258/http://www.multicrop.com.au/MSDS/Scat_MSDS.doc | dead-url = no }}.</ref><ref>{{citation | url = http://www.tandridge.gov.uk/environment/pestcontrol/foxes.htm | title = Pest Control: Foxes | publisher = Tandridge District Council (UK) | date = February 2006 | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | archive-date = 2010-05-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100528182233/http://www.tandridge.gov.uk/environment/pestcontrol/foxes.htm | dead-url = no }}.</ref>。

==毒性==
硫酸铝铵中的[[硫酸鋁|硫酸鋁]]，是無毒的，{{LD50}}為6207 mg/kg。沒有註冊為對人類或是環境（低濃度下）有毒的物質<ref>{{citation | title = PAN Pesticide Database | url = http://www.pesticideinfo.org/Detail_Chemical.jsp?Rec_Id=PC33857 | contribution = Ammonium alum | publisher = Pesticides Action Network | accessdate = 2009-11-23 | archive-date = 2009-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091127005035/http://www.pesticideinfo.org/Detail_Chemical.jsp?Rec_Id=PC33857 | dead-url = no }}.</ref>。

